She says, oh, I wanna
just go straight to sleep.

00:24:58.297 --> 00:25:00.132 align:middle line:84%
>> You may assume that
the longer you sleep,

00:25:00.132 --> 00:25:01.800 align:middle line:90%
the more rested you'll be.

00:25:01.800 --> 00:25:04.203 align:middle line:84%
While it's clearly important
to get enough sleep,

00:25:04.203 --> 00:25:07.072 align:middle line:84%
going to bed at the right
time, when your body is ready,

00:25:07.072 --> 00:25:08.707 align:middle line:90%
is just as important.

00:25:12.177 --> 00:25:13.645 align:middle line:90%
>> Hi, dad.

00:25:27.993 --> 00:25:32.231 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm certainly no
stranger to lack of sleep.

